<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=5 f=1 -->
17
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

</FOOTNAME>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
Proposed paragraph (b)(5)(i) would also contain a proviso that it ``shall not be construed to prohibit a statement
that a person is included on a list of ethics training providers maintained by a registered futures association if
such statement is true in fact and if the effect of such a listing is not misrepresented.'' The effect of this statement
is intended to be that such person is not precluded from providing ethics training by reason of ``unfitness'' as defined
by the Act and the Commission's rules on statutory disqualification.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->
</FOOTNOTE>

