<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Nor should an ethics training provider proffer evidence of that fact in order to demonstrate experience, competence
or knowledge that would qualify the provider as an expert witness in any adjudicatory proceeding to which the Commission
