<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
The Commission is also proposing under revised paragraph (b)(4) of Rule 3.34 that records of trainer evaluations
be maintained. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</FOOTNOTE>

