<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
EPA will consider all public comments on its tentative determination received during the public comment period.
Issues raised by those comments may be the basis for a decision to deny final approval to South Dakota. EPA expects to
make a final decision on whether or not to approve South Dakota's program by October 20, 1994 and will give notice of
it in the 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=4 -->
