(1) Proof of ownership.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) A detailed statement of the amount claimed.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) An itemized receipt of payment for necessary repairs or itemized written estimates of the cost of such repairs.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(4) A statement listing date of purchase, purchase price, and salvage value where repair is not economical.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(5) Any other evidence or information which may have a bearing on either the responsibility of the United States for
the injury to or loss of property or the damages claimed.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

